#Creational Design Pattern

	the way of creating objects
	the decision taken at the time of creating object

~ Using new keyword is not best approach, it must be flexible 

# Types of creational design pattern

1. Factory Method Pattern

	define an interface or abstract class & let the subclasses decide which class to instantiate.

# Usage 
	s
	When a class doesn't know what sub-classes will be required to create
	When a class wants that its sub-classes specify the objects to be created.
	When the parent classes choose the creation of objects to its sub-classes.